goals.question: What is the distribution of body mass across different penguin genders?

goals.question: What is the distribution of beak length across different penguin islands?

import seaborn as sns
import pandas as pd
import matplotlib.pyplot as plt

def plot(data: pd.DataFrame):
    chart = sns.boxplot(x="Species", y="Body_Mass__g_", data=data)
    plt.title("What is the distribution of body mass across different penguin species?", wrap=True)
    chart.axhline(data['Body_Mass__g_'].median(), color='r', linestyle='--', label='Median: {:.2f}'.format(data['Body_Mass__g_'].median()))
    chart.legend(loc='upper left')
    return plt;

chart = plot(data)
